# CODEOWNERS — map folders to reviewers.
#
# When a team forms, replace the placeholder @cory-sharplin owner on each
# line with the appropriate team handle (e.g. @acme-org/platform-team).
# GitHub auto-requests review from the owner(s) listed for any file a PR
# touches. Most-specific rule wins, so put broad catch-alls first and
# narrow overrides below.
#
# Docs: https://docs.github.com/en/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-security/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners

# ── Catch-all ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
